snippet.title: Beasts of Burden Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Beasts of Burden is a psychological horror RPG and ARG inspired by a certain popular RPG for the Gameboy Advance. Use WASD to move and the Space bar to interact in this simple but engaging horror experience. This game is still in development but you can enjoy this small demo and look forward to the full game expected to release on September 10th.

Play the demo now: https://audiodread.itch.io/beasts-of-burden
Support the game on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/KeirdanJenson

Find me on twitter:
https://twitter.com/audio_dread
